- The program assumes the SHT31 sensor is connected to the default I2C address (`0x44`). Adjust the address if your setup differs.
- Error handling is included for I2C initialization and data reads.
- The program appends data to `environmental_log.json`. If you want to overwrite the file each time, change the mode to `w` instead of `a`.
