3. **Seven-Segment Display Configuration**: Ensure your seven-segment display is properly connected to the 74HC595 shift register.

### Wiring Diagram:
- **74HC595 Shift Register**:
  - DS (Data) -> GPIO 0 (pin 12)
  - SH_CP (Shift Clock) -> GPIO 1 (pin 31)
  - ST_CP (Storage Clock) -> GPIO 2 (pin 32)
  - SRCLR (Serial Clear) -> Ground
  - OE (Output Enable) -> GPIO 3 (pin 33)

- **Seven-Segment Display**:
  - A -> GPIO 4 (pin 7)
  - B -> GPIO 5 (pin 8)
  - C -> GPIO 6 (pin 9)
  - D -> GPIO 7 (pin 10)
  - E -> GPIO 8 (pin 11)
  - F -> GPIO 9 (pin 12)
  - G -> GPIO 10 (pin 13)

